enhanced_by.reason: The constructor initializes the ResultSet and RowProcessor, which are essential for the hasNext method to function correctly.
The iterable method creates an instance of ResultSetIterator, which is necessary to call the hasNext method.
The next method also interacts with the ResultSet and can be used to verify the state of the ResultSet after calling hasNext.
The toArray method from BasicRowProcessor can be used to verify the contents of the ResultSet after calling hasNext.
